translations: vi.加入国籍；归化（等于 naturalize）

sentences.sentence: I will also remember to get C 'Rose Queen', as it is one of the nicest for naturalising, and I plan to have it coming up with Cyclamen hederifolium under a grove of open magnolias.
sentences.translation: 我还不会忘记去订购“玫瑰女皇”，这是供移栽的最好的一种花，我计划将它与仙客来一起种在开阔的木兰花树丛底下。
